item.title: ICURFC 3rd XV’s fresher Ridge builds up an appetite
item.author: Will Cox,
item.description: Imperial 3rd XV 59 - 27 UWL 1st XV Wednesday was a big day for the 3s in several aspects. After a tough loss the previous week, some changes to the squad, and only a few substitutes, it was integral that everyone plays to their best form.
